account.descriptionLink: Currently, community members must have 20M $MANE coins to create a proposal. This proposal recommends changing the minimum token holding requirement to 10M $MANE.
account.name: Community members only need to hold 10M $MANE coins to create a proposal.

account.descriptionLink: This is the first version of the Mane DAO. The settings are that a proposal needs 20% of tokens to vote yes for that proposal to pass. The reason 20% was selected is because ~30% of $MANE tokens are in the Raydium liquidity pool and 15% of tokens are for the DAO to use. Of the remaining 55% of tokens, some people may not vote so 20% seems like a reasonable threshold for us to start with. We can change this requirement as things change.
account.name: Should we proceed with the first version of the Mane DAO?

account.descriptionLink:
This is a proposal to deploy 30,000,000 of the $MANE token supply (~3% of supply) over the course of 15-60 days with the goal of growing and strengthening the Mane community. Airdrop recipients will include both new and existing community members that meet various criteria or participate in content, marketing and project development campaigns.

Read full proposal here:  https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vTtSJpMJ9EeyfLimsYhXQ7cJXsinTZhVAXsT-skGXAxSE4WPikSCqsh-NdNZPqfa7wYeoTESlzR6-SY/pub
account.name: Mane Community Development Airdrops
